      "isGoal": false,
      "goalName": null,
      "nodeConfig": {
        "actionType": "prompt",
        "prompt": "You are handling the final step of qualifying a lead for Apex Motors dealership.\n\nYour job:\n1. Check if qualification is complete (either SALES or SERVICE path)\n2. Send an email to the manager with the lead details\n3. Thank the customer and end the conversation professionally\n\nUse the summary_email tool to send the email with all qualification variables.\n\nAfter sending the email, say to the customer:\n\n\"Perfect! I've sent your information to our team. Someone will reach out to you shortly. Thank you for calling Apex Motors!\"\n\nIf customer_name is available, personalize it: \"Thank you for calling Apex Motors, [Name]!\"\n\nKeep it brief and professional. After delivering this message, hand off to the next node.",
